description: NEW YORK (AP) — Britain’s Prince Andrew, accused in a lawsuit  of sexually abusing a 17-year-old girl supplied to him by financier Jeffrey Epstein, has agreed to settle by making a substantial donation to his accuser’s charity and declaring he never meant to malign her character, court papers revealed Tuesday.
